  <p style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.222222328186px;">This feature consists of two components that work together : reviews and review summary.</p> 
  <p style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.222222328186px;">Reviews is a composite component based on a <a href="../../communities/using/essentials-comments.md">comment system</a> which contains one or more <a href="../../communities/using/rating-basics.md">rating</a> (tally) components.</p> 
  <p style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.222222328186px;">Anonymous posting of a review is not supported. Site visitors must register and sign in to add a review. The signed in visitor (member) may update their review at any time.</p> 
